author: @spammeat1730
text: Tip: If you want the ability to have the domain automatically redirect from www.domain.com and domain.com with https, you'll need to save your server in nginx/sites-enables/app_name as domain.com (without the www) before you enable Let's Encrypt. Then it'll give you the option for both www.domain.com and domain.com. Thanks again Corey!
